ucts under the India Gate, Nur Jahan, Zabreen, Bemisal, Uplife, Aarati, Unity, Rameez, Lion, and other brands. The company was formerly known as Khushi Ram Behari Lal Limited and changed its name to KRBL Limited in February 2000. The company was founded in 1889 and is based in Noida, India."}}